# CLaaS2SaaS Enterprise Control Center — UI Style Audit

> **Date**: 2026-03-05  
> **Scope**: `apps/web/src/`  
> **Purpose**: Read-only analysis. No files were modified.

---

## STEP 1 — STYLE SOURCES INVENTORY

| Source | Type | Path |
|---|---|---|
| `colors.css` | CSS Variables (design tokens) | `src/theme/colors.css` |
| `kernelTheme.ts` | Fluent UI brand ramp (TS object) | `src/theme/kernelTheme.ts` |
| `index.css` | Global reset / font import | `src/styles/index.css` |
| `topbar-vanilla.css` | Plain CSS — TopBar component | `src/app/topbar-vanilla.css` |
| `SignInPage.module.css` | CSS Module | `src/features/auth/pages/` |
| `RoleManagementPage.module.css` | CSS Module | `src/features/role-management/pages/` |
| `AddSecurityRoleModal.module.css` | CSS Module | `src/features/role-management/components/` |
| `EditSecurityRoleModal.module.css` | CSS Module | `src/features/role-management/components/` |
| `AddUserModal.module.css` | CSS Module | `src/features/user-enrichment/components/` |
| `EditUserModal.module.css` | CSS Module | `src/features/user-enrichment/components/` |
| `UserEnrichmentPage.module.css` | CSS Module | `src/features/user-enrichment/pages/` |
| Griffel `makeStyles()` | CSS-in-JS (Fluent UI v9) | All `*.tsx` component files |
| Hardcoded inline `style={{}}` | JSX inline styles | Multiple `*.tsx` files |

> **No Tailwind**. No SCSS. No styled-components. No emotion.

