## STEP 3 — TYPOGRAPHY SYSTEM

### Font Families

| Font | Where Loaded | Used In |
|---|---|---|
| `Montserrat` (wght 300,400,600,700,800,900) | `@import` in `index.css` | `SignInPage` only |
| `Source Sans 3` (wght 300,400,600) | `@import` in `index.css` | `SignInPage` only |
| `-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Ubuntu` (system stack) | `index.css` body rule | All app pages |
| `Inter, system-ui, sans-serif` | Hardcoded in `AuditLogViewerPage.tsx` Griffel | Audit pages only |

> [!WARNING]
> **No `Inter` import exists in `index.css`**. The `AuditLogViewerPage` declares `fontFamily: 'Inter, system-ui, sans-serif'` in Griffel but the font is never loaded — the browser will fall back to `system-ui`. `Inter` should be added to the Google Fonts import.

### Font Sizes

| Element | Size | Weight | Source |
|---|---|---|---|
| Audit page title | `28px` | `600` | `AuditLogViewerPage.tsx` |
| Role Management page title | `24px` | `600` | `RoleManagementPage.tsx` |
| UserEnrichment page title | `22px` | `600` | `UserEnrichmentPage.module.css` |
| Page subtitle | `14px` | `400` | Multiple files |
| Table header `th` | `13px` | `600` | Audit, Role, UserEnrich pages |
| Table cell primary | `13px` | `600` | Multiple |
| Table cell secondary | `12px` | `400` | Multiple |
| Table cell text | `13–14px` | `400–500` | Multiple |
| Permission badge | `11px` | `600` | `AuditLogViewerPage.tsx` |
| Status badge | `12px` | `600` | Multiple |
| Nav brand | `1rem` | `600` | `topbar-vanilla.css` |
| Nav search | `0.875rem` | `400` | `topbar-vanilla.css` |
| Nav env label | `0.65rem` | `400` | `topbar-vanilla.css` |
| Nav env name | `0.8rem` | `500` | `topbar-vanilla.css` |
| Sign-in brand name | `52px` | `900` | `SignInPage.module.css` |
| Sign-in card heading | `26px` | `800` | `SignInPage.module.css` |
| Footer / count text | `12–13px` | `400` | Multiple |

